@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Upload an image as a chat message
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/media
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="text"

Here is a picture
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload a video as a chat message
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/media
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="text"

Here is a short video
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./sample.mp4
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--
